not to be able to leave. You are coming to know more and more about 
us. I suggest you join because otherwise, we will have to kill you. We 
are members of the Tripredacus, a faction of transformers parallel to 
the Predacons. This renegade jeopardizes our plans, thus we were sent 
to take care of him. You look intelligent, Windlord, and someone with 
a head is always welcome around here.
